            <a href="http://www.sauropodstudio.com/">Sauropod Studio</a> |
            <a href="http://www.joachimdespland.com">Joachim Despland</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="span3">
            <p>Copyright &copy; 2012 KO-OP Mode Inc.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

